#. js-lingui-id: XEEpNj
#: src/platform/releases/release-notes.tsx
msgid "You can now visualize your records in a monthly calendar view. This new view type makes it easy to track time-based data like events, deadlines, and scheduled activities directly within any object."
msgstr "You can now visualize your records in a monthly calendar view. This new view type makes it easy to track time-based data like events, deadlines, and scheduled activities directly within any object."

